Global EM
Edward Robertson


 Key Facts

Team orientated investment approach pioneered in the 1990s.
Conviction-driven portfolios (c. 40 stocks).
Bottom up research intensive process essential to risk control.
We are aiming to achieve a balance between growth and value in all our positions.
























Dilution Levy  | Somerset Capital Management
































